{"product_id":"berrichi-face-wash-foam-150ml","title":"BERRICHI Face Wash Foam 150ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDiscover the perfect balance between effective cleansing and gentle care. Berrich Facial Cleansing Foam is designed to provide your skin with the care of nature. It gently cleanses away dirt and make-up residue, leaving your skin’s natural balance undisturbed for a clean, velvety complexion.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAlso suitable for removing thin make-up\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for everyday use\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRemoves dirt and residues from the skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGently exfoliating\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eContains anti-ageing ingredients\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLeaves skin feeling fresh and clean\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLime Pearl™ extract\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– contains natural AHA acids. They gently exfoliate dead skin cells, leaving skin soft, smooth and radiant.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to damp skin, massaging gently in circular motions for at least 30 seconds, then rinse thoroughly. If you leave the foam on for a longer time, it will act as a gentle exfoliating face mask.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua (Water), Glycerin, Disodium\/Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate (Protelan AG 37), Lauroyl\/Myristoyl Methyl Glucamide (Glucotain Flex), Decyl Glucoside (ELOTANT MILCOSIDE 302), Polyglyceryl-6 Caprylate\/Polyglyceryl-3 Cocoate\/Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate\/Polyglyceryl-6 Ricinoleate (TEGO® Solve 61), Glycerin\/Water\/Microcitrus Australasica Fruit Extract (LIME PEARL™ AF), Capryloyl\/Caproyl Anhydro Methyl Glucamide\/Water (Velsan® Flex), Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil (Organic Jojoba Oil)*, Potassium Sorbate, Furcellaria Lumbricalis extract (Furcellaran), Citric Acid, Haematococcus pluvialis\/Tocopherol (Astaxanthin oil).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084200968519,"sku":null,"price":26.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-face-wash-foam-150ml-999971.png?v=1739979952","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/berrichi-face-wash-foam-150ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}